{"id":330193,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/global-voices-照片集：印尼锡纳朋火山爆发-逾两万人撤离/","date":"2014-01-18T05:30:21Z","modified":"2014-01-18T05:30:21Z","title":"Global Voices | 照片集：印尼锡纳朋火山爆发  逾两万人撤离","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/3644588/sinabung-eruption-indonesia-form-drawing-skull-human\"><img alt=\"Mount Sinabung erupted when a cloud of dust and heat to form an image of human skull. Photo by Abdullah Arief Siregar, Copyright @Demotix (1/9/2014)\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/skull-800x533.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>锡纳朋火山爆发的火山灰形成人脸的影像。照片来自 Abdullah Arief Siregar，Demotix 版权（1/9/2014）</p>\n</div>\n<p>印尼北苏门答腊的锡纳朋火山自去年以来已<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2014/01/140109-volcano-mount-sinabung-erupting-indonesia-ash-lava/?utm_source=Twitter&#038;utm_medium=Social&#038;utm_content=link_tw20140109news-mountsina&#038;utm_campaign=Content\">喷发</a>超过两百次，迫使超过两万村民<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/news/mt-sinabung-volcano-erupts-30-times-as-20000-displaced/\">撤离</a>。这座火山自西元 1600 起一直处于<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.tempo.co/read/news/2013/11/21/206531575/Central-Javas-Sleeping-Volcanoes-Potentially-Active--\">休眠</a>状态。</p>\n<p>发现火山（Volcano Discovery）提供了锡纳朋火山最新的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.volcanodiscovery.com/sinabung/news.html#.Us9Prbks8Ic.twitter\">活动报告</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>不断增长的熔岩穹丘，不稳定、黏稠度中等的岩浆，部分区域频繁塌陷造成高温岩浆块和火山灰崩塌（火山碎屑流），距离可达 4.5 公里。根据最新数据，从五到七公里疏散区撤出的难民已达两万五千人。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>位于环太平洋火山带的印尼有超过一百座活火山，但 Carl 相信锡纳朋火山只会造成<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://volcanocafe.wordpress.com/2014/01/06/the-road-to-sinabung/\">中型</a>喷发：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>锡纳朋底下的岩浆体系绝没有足够的岩浆产生大爆发。</p>\n<p>既然我们对这座火山的了解极少，也许应该观察附近的火山以推测它的状态。数公里外的席巴亚克/平托双火山可能可以给我们一些线索。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>当局下令<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/news/authorities-warn-residents-against-returning-to-villages-near-mount-sinabung/\">撤离</a>居民，并承诺受影响民众，会很快将援助送到<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2014/01/06/worst-case-scenario-being-prepared-mt-sinabung.html\">避难所</a>。但除了撤离的居民之外，锡纳朋火山喷发也严重影响了当地的农业。</p>\n<p>Utami Irawati 对受到火山爆发影响的民众表达支持：</p>\n<blockquote lang=\"en\">\n<p>Thoughts and prayers for people around Sinabung. Stay strong, and I sincerely pray that things will get better soon :”(</p>\n<p>— Utami Irawati (@utamiirawati) <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/utamiirawati/statuses/420582697212182528\">January 7, 2014</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote lang=\"en\">\n<p>为锡纳朋一带的民众祈祷。要坚强，我诚心祈祷事情很快会好转  :”(</p>\n<p>— Utami Irawati (@utamiirawati) 2014 年一月七日</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>以下来自 Demotix 的照片展现锡纳朋火山将<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://qz.com/163811/indonesia-sumatra-mount-sinabung-volcano-erupted-77-times-in-a-single-day/\">火山灰</a>和岩浆喷上半空。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/3616230/mount-sinabung-erupts-indonesia\"><img alt=\"Mount Sinabung ejected lava and hot clouds over Berastepu and Bakerah villages. Photo by by Abdullah Arief Siregar, Copyright @Demotix (1/5/2014)\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/lava-800x533.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>锡纳朋火山喷出岩浆和高温烟尘，笼罩 Berastepu 和 Bakerah 村。照片来自 Abdullah Arief Siregar，Demotix 版权（1/5/2014）</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/3622044/indonesia-harvests-covered-ash-sinabung-volcano#media-3621961\"><img alt=\"Farmers harvest tomatoes covered in a thick layer of ash from the eruption of Mt. Sinabung. Photo by Ahmad Ridwan Nasution, Copyright @Demotix (1/6/2014)\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/harvest-800x533.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>农人采收被厚厚一层锡纳朋火山喷出的灰烬覆盖的蕃茄。照片来自 Ahmad Ridwan Nasution，Demotix 版权（1/6/2014）</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/3344420/sinabung-volcano-continues-erupt-indonesian#media-3342090\"><img alt=\"The eruption of Mount Sinabung on November 24, 2013 ejected ash in the air with a height of about 10,000km. Photo by Abdullah Arief Siregar, Copyright @Demotix (11/24/2013)\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/eruption.jpg\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\"></a></p>\n<p>2013 年十一月廿四日锡纳朋火山爆发，喷出的火山灰高达一万公尺。照片来自 Abdullah Arief Siregar，Demotix 版权（11/24/2013）</p>\n</div>\n<div>校对：Fen</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/hllee/\" title=\"文章导读 Hsu-Lei Lee\">Hsu-Lei Lee</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2014/01/11/photos-mount-sinabung-eruption-displaced-20000-in-indonesia/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2014/01/18/13105/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E9%94%A1%E7%BA%B3%E6%9C%8B%E7%81%AB%E5%B1%B1%E7%88%86%E5%8F%91++%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%A4%E7%A6%BB&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2014%2F01%2F18%2F13105%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2014%2F01%2F18%2F13105%2F&#